&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;A Solution to Help Curb Data Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CHICAGOWhen it comes to hospitality, you can never be too careful. Data breaches at hotels are widespread and hackers are not just hitting up the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://m.hotelbusiness.com/Other/A-Solution-to-Help-Curb-Data-Breaches/56556&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://m.hotelbusiness.com/Other/A-Solution-to-Help-Curb-Data-Breaches/56556&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;A cybersecurity risk assessment is a critical part of M&amp;amp;A due diligence&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The economic impact of a transaction can shift dramatically if, after the deal is consummated, past or ongoing data breaches come to light. The NYSE &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.networkworld.com/article/3182139/security/a-cybersecurity-risk-assessment-is-a-critical-part-of-manda-due-diligence.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.networkworld.com/article/3182139/security/a-cybersecurity-risk-assessment-is-a-critical-part-of-manda-due-diligence.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Specialised security detection services threaten traditional MSSPs&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This has allowed new sub-sectors to emerge, including deception, endpoint detection and response (EDR), software-defined segmentation, cloud &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.channelpro.co.uk/news/10374/specialised-security-detection-services-threaten-traditional-mssps&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.channelpro.co.uk/news/10374/specialised-security-detection-services-threaten-traditional-mssps&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Video Roundup: New in data breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Revealed: New York airport&amp;rsquo;s wave of security lapses. US and UK intelligence allegedly hacked smart TVs for surveillance purposes. Easily hacked &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.zdnet.com/article/video-roundup-new-in-data-breaches/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.zdnet.com/article/video-roundup-new-in-data-breaches/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

