&lt;p&gt;Teamwork is a key to advancing in the Big Dance and HR and IT could make a powerful team in fighting cybersecurity risks in your company.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.natlawreview.com/article/avoiding-employee-data-breaches-has-nothing-to-do-luck&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.natlawreview.com/article/avoiding-employee-data-breaches-has-nothing-to-do-luck&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

